
load ../string
  take form string

form error
  base message, form string

task create
  base message

  call make
    bind constructor, text <Error>
    bind factor, link message
    turn seed

task get-stack
  base error, form error

  call get-aspect
    bind object, link error
    bind aspect, text <stack>
    turn seed

task throw
  base message, form string

  call throw-error
    bind factor, link message
